ZH: 1. 巡视是领导对工作情况进行检查和指导的重要方式。
EN: 1. Inspection is an important way for leaders to inspect and guide work situations.
ZH: 2. 他每天都会巡视工厂的生产线，确保生产进程顺利进行。
EN: 2. He inspects the production line of the factory every day to ensure smooth progress.
ZH: 3. 为了确保公共安全，警察会定期巡视街道。
EN: 3. To ensure public safety, police officers regularly patrol the streets.
ZH: 4. 参观园区时，请跟随导游的巡视路线。
EN: 4. When visiting the park, please follow the tour guide's designated route.
ZH: 5. 巡视组正在对该公司的财务报表进行核查。
EN: 5. The inspection team is conducting an audit of the company's financial statements.
ZH: 6. 军官在营区巡视，确保士兵们的纪律严明。
EN: 6. The officer patrols the barracks to ensure strict discipline among the soldiers.
ZH: 7. 检察官定期到监狱巡视，监督犯罪分子的生活状况。
EN: 7. Prosecutors regularly visit prisons to supervise the living conditions of criminals.
ZH: 8. 这支队伍每天都会巡视校园，保护学生的安全。
EN: 8. This team patrols the campus every day to ensure the safety of students.
ZH: 9. 基层干部在晚上巡视社区，防止违法行为发生。
EN: 9. Grassroots cadres patrol the community at night to prevent illegal activities.
ZH: 10. 巡视任务要求我们对现场环境进行仔细观察和记录。
EN: 10. The inspection task requires us to carefully observe and document the on-site environment.
ZH: 11. 城市交通警察巡视路口，维护交通秩序。
EN: 11. Urban traffic police patrol intersections to maintain traffic order.
ZH: 12. 巡视的目的是发现并解决工作中存在的问题。
EN: 12. The purpose of inspection is to identify and solve problems in the work.
ZH: 13. 建筑监理负责巡视施工现场，确保工程质量。
EN: 13. The construction supervisor is responsible for inspecting the construction site to ensure the quality of the project.
ZH: 14. 巡视员负责对食品生产设施进行例行检查。
EN: 14. The inspector is responsible for conducting routine inspections of food production facilities.
ZH: 15. 巡视小组将调查这个单位的腐败现象。
EN: 15. The inspection team will investigate the corruption in this organization.
ZH: 16. 巡视员要对工作人员的表现进行评估和指导。
EN: 16. The inspector needs to assess and guide the performance of the staff.
ZH: 17. 政府官员巡视灾区，分发救灾物资。
EN: 17. Government officials tour the disaster-stricken areas and distribute relief supplies.
ZH: 18. 巡视队会定期对边境线进行巡视，以防止非法入境。
EN: 18. The patrol team regularly inspects the border to prevent illegal entry.
ZH: 19. 巡视会议汇报了营地安全情况和应急准备工作。
EN: 19. The inspection meeting reported on the camp's safety situation and emergency preparedness.
ZH: 20. 高层领导将亲自巡视基地，了解员工的工作环境。
EN: 20. Top leaders will personally inspect the base to understand the working environment of the employees.
